### Hermite like polynomials with middle node

Define linear forms

::: {#1c8dc7f8 .cell execution_count=8}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
struct ValueAt <: AbstractMapping{AbstractMapping,Real,AllOf{AbstractMapping}()}
    x::Real
end
MMJMesh.Mathematics.valueat(u::ValueAt, f) = f(u.x)

struct DerivativeAt <: AbstractMapping{AbstractMapping,Real,AllOf{AbstractMapping}()}
    x::Real
end
MMJMesh.Mathematics.valueat(u::DerivativeAt, f) = f'(u.x)
```
:::


Compute polynomials

::: {#3e6daead .cell execution_count=9}
``` {.julia .cell-code}
h = 2.0
N = [ValueAt.(0:h/2:h); DerivativeAt.([0, h])] |> vcat
P = monomials(0:length(N)-1, 0 .. h)
M = [n(p) for p in P, n in N]
H = inv(M) * P
plot(H...)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=10}
![](mathematics_files/figure-html/cell-10-output-1.svg){}
:::
